
    CHRISTMAS ended on a tragic note for a Malawian family when a toddler lost her life after her dad attacked her mum.According to Nyasa Times, Chikumbutso Galu (30) from Galu village in southern Malawi lost his temper with his wife, Paula Devani (27) on Monday night because she couldn’t explain what happened to the money he had given her.Nsanje Police Public relations officer, Sergeant Agnes Zalakoma is quoted in the story as saying: “After the quarrel, the husband picked up a panga and wanted to hit his wife with it. Unfortunately, the knife landed on the head of the daughter who sustained a big cut and later died.” if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjssx_O8RgmoLcjKZmcROZFzUyeJzPAT7stAYv12o159ucbIxV0cX3jBcETpk0l4xD3UBMgzrM-VfuvutnUPrQnrwfykAq2LS6BE4lTYBIcIy9bZrG4lqcWD9ij0C8ct7cjW6sad2XcpO8tQRV4j-FMzlx7oueg3YGApmlpUx59ZssOBGK9cbo7hLGfg2a9d-lBVGNYO3CzIZojs_wrJkCwkn9YH6kX6j8eWi0LnKaZcmO-FKdrZVBg1BHGyYuahCV8xCFDQmeQUIRbSCv5s2M5NLfwcRS2bo_6GMAQ\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzBboN-cjmlh7EAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
